products.title: Ash Grey Real Wood
products.description: Ourpremium quality sunwood range ofblinds are one of the leading wooden venetian blind brands in the uk market - we are confident you will not buy better quality blinds, backed by their 3 year guarantee. All blinds are sent with installation instructions, universal bracket (top fix, side fix or face fix) and a pelmet fascia to sit on the front of the blind headrail. The ash grey blinds are made using an all natural wood which is simply beautiful, from the sunwood range.

products.title: Ash Perfect Fit Sunwood
products.description: This handsome perfect fit sunwood blind comes in a range of great fabrics - here we have it in ash. In addition, this blind includes controls to the left, no frame and no brackets (which are all options).
